# ============================================================================
# FLARE NETWORK CONFIGURATION
# ============================================================================
# This file contains all Flare-specific environment variables for the
# Gas Fountain platform integration with Flare Network technologies:
# - FTSOv2 (Flare Time Series Oracle) for price feeds
# - FDC (Flare Data Connector) for cross-chain attestations
# - FAssets for wrapped non-smart contract assets (BTC, DOGE, XRP)
